title: Cal Smart Barramundi Bistro Salad with Buttered Garlic Potatoes
description: Our take on a classic bistro salad proves you can have all the flavours of French dining in the comfort of your own home! Flaky, pan-fried barramundi is an elegant topper for a crisp spinach salad, complete with marinated shallots, a mustard vinaigrette and buttery parsley potatoes.

